[
  "Michaela Herz owns 27% of the private equity firm Mayfair SE, whose investments have included the sports apparel company Puma.",
  "She is the granddaughter of Tchibo co-founder Max Herz, who built a fortune based on the importation and sale of coffee.",
  "Her father, Guenter, ran Tchibo for almost 35 years. The family also built a stake in skin-care company Beiersdorf, whose brands include Nivea.",
  "Guenter and his sister, Daniela Herz-Schnoeckel, founded Mayfair after they were bought out of the family business in 2003.",
  "As one of Mayfair's managing directors, Michaela Herz is active in the shaping investment decisions."
